    "If the amount of data displayed in the list is too large, disabling image preview can improve performance. Enabling image preview in the list allows you to view copied images." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果列表中显示的数据量过大，可以禁用图片预览以提升性能。在列表中启用图片预览可以查看已复制的图片。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If the save limit exceeds the existing data quantity, %@ will gradually reduce the excess, rather than clearing all the extra data at once." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "保存数量若超过已有数据数量，%@ 将逐步递减超出的部分，而不会一次性清空多余的数据。"
